      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JOHNNY SPROCKETS (4) is progressing well scoring last time out (19.70) at this track and bringing up his 3rd career win. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Ideally placed to take this out. FINE VIEW (1) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including four wins and five placings. Was out of the placings last time (31.78) at this track in a Grade 6, finishing sixth and beaten 14 lengths. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. MASTER KILCOY (2) had been going along well winning a Grade 6 three back then placing at Gawler before missing the frame latest when fourth (20.17) at this track. Has good speed and aided by a low draw. Rates a winning chance on best. BRISTOL MOSS (8) was in the money last start and wasn't beaten far - poses a threat again.",
